      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been super well-loved? This beauty is in great shape and ready for all your upcoming adventures! It runs like a dream and has been a joy to own, but it's time for it to find a new home. I\u2019ve taken really good care of it, and I\u2019d love for you to come take it for a spin! Feel free to reach out with any questions at all\u2014I'm here to help! \u2728",
