      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Available for the discerning driver is this 2004 BMW M3 (E46). At its core lies the S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and high-pressure VANOS to achieve a high-revving, linear power delivery. This specimen is equipped with the tactile Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and an M Variable Differential Lock for superior corner-exit traction. The subframe has been proactively reinforced, addressing a known E46 weak point, while the suspension retains its factory-spec damping and compliance. Recent service includes a valve adjustment and rod bearing clearance check. This is a mechanically sound driver\u2019s car, offering the visceral feedback and chassis balance that defined an era of German engineering.",
      "price": 34500.0,
